<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n10042a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n10" href="#n10042a">N10 (VI.B.16)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n10all.htm#n10042a"> 42(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> make it hot</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><b>The Open Forum</b> <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> Cruelty to Children and Animals Sir,&mdash;<font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> The general public should always bear this in mind that any brutal outrage brings discredit and shame not only on the vile perpetrators, but on the whole district <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> Therefore they ought not to be content with mere passive objection but should as far as possible <mark>&ldquo;make it hot&rdquo;</mark> for the scoundrels <small> <a name="CT12apr24" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CT12apr24"><cite title="source">Connacht Tribune</cite></a> (12 April 1924) 7/5</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
